===Proper noun===
'''Nenets''' (ISO 639-2: '''mis'''; ISO 639-3: '''yrk''')
# a member of a people who live in the extreme northwest of [[Russia]]; the [[Samoyed]].
# the [[Samoyedic]] [[language]] spoken by these people.

